2005-01-07  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yoda.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/Relation.h, lib/Relation.cc:
	o Member method invert() no longer const! It inverts the current object.
	o New static method invert (const Relation&) that returns a new
	  inverted relation.
	o Stacking annotation revised to assign one of the four new stacking
	  types.
	o Additonal pairing annotation for base flips
	o Method is(const PropertyType*) also checks for specialized types,
	  new method has(const PropertyType*) checks only for a specific type.
	o New method reset()
	o New annotation identification as any combination of the three
	  main familes: adjacent, stacking and pairing.

	* lib/PropertyTypeStore.h, lib/PropertyTypeStore.cc, lib/PropertyType.h, lib/PropertyType.cc:
	Modifications in the hierarchy:

	o Adjacent5p and Adjacent3p both extend Adjacent, making DIR_5p and
	  DIR_3p obsolete (removed along with DIR_ANY).

	o Additional pairing information about base plane flips: Straight and
	  Reverse (as in a standard helical Watson-Crick). Cis and Trans
	  annotation was kept (for now...).

	o New stacking labeling:

	   BaseOrientation          Stack
	          |                   |
	     +----+----+         +----+----+
	     |         |         |         |
	  Straight  Reverse    Upward   Downward
	     |         |         |         |
	     +---+---------------+         |
	     |   |     |         |         |
	     +------+----------------------+
	         |  |  |         |         |
	         |  |  +----+----+         |
	         |  |  |    |              |
	         |  |  +--------+----------+
	         |  |       |   |
	         |  |       |   +-- ReverseDownward
	         |  |       +------ ReverseUpward
	         |  +-------------- StraightDownward
	         +----------------- StraigthUpward

	* lib/Residue.cc: *** empty log message ***

	* lib/HomogeneousTransfo.h, lib/HomogeneousTransfo.cc:
	Added two optional float* parameters to the distance metric methods to
	save both contributions from translation and rotation for analysis.

	* lib/Binstream.h, lib/Binstream.cc:
	Using unsigned int for string length instead of short int

	* lib/Exception.cc: *** empty log message ***

2005-01-06  Martin Larose  <larosem@yoda.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/RnamlReader.cc, lib/Relation.h, lib/Relation.cc, lib/Molecule.h, lib/Molecule.cc, lib/ModelFactoryMethod.h, lib/ModelFactoryMethod.cc, lib/Model.h, lib/Model.cc, lib/Makefile.in, lib/GraphModel.h, lib/GraphModel.cc:
	ModelFactoryMethods added for GraphModel and Model.  Weird bug on copy constructor corrected in GraphModel and Model.

2005-01-05  Martin Larose  <larosem@yoda.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/RnamlWriter.cc: Added the try/catch on getProperty.

	* lib/Residue.h, lib/Residue.cc:
	Moved the constants in the header.  Reordered the initialisations.

	* lib/Pdbstream.cc: Minor changes.

	* lib/Molecule.h, lib/Molecule.cc:
	Moved the ostream operator<< in std namespace.  Changed the getProperty method to string parameter and return value.  getProperty throws NoSuchElementException instead of the less specific IntLibException.

	* lib/Model.cc: Minor changes.

	* lib/Model.h, lib/GraphModel.h:
	The clone operator needs the cast.  If not it gives weird behavior (and bugs).

	* lib/ExtendedResidue.h, lib/ExtendedResidue.cc:
	*** empty log message ***

	* lib/Binstream.h, lib/Binstream.cc:
	Added the operators << and >> on strings.

	* lib/Atom.h, lib/Atom.cc:
	Moved the ostream operator<< in std namespace.

	* lib/AbstractModel.cc: *** empty log message ***

