2004-12-29  Martin Larose  <larosem@onyx.glyphe.net>

	* lib/Model.h, lib/Model.cc [GraphModel]: Copy constructor and
	assignment are with AbstractModel instead of only GraphModel.  erase
	deletes the Residue pointer.

	* lib/Messagestream.h [GraphModel]: bool operator<< added.  The
	std::operator<< is specifically called on template
	Messagestream::operator<<.

	* lib/GraphModel.h, lib/GraphModel.cc [GraphModel]: Copy constructor
	and assignment are with AbstractModel instead of only GraphModel.
	Vertex and edge weights are int (for now).

	* lib/Exception.cc [GraphModel]: File and line output is made only
	when they exists :-)

	* lib/AtomSet.h, lib/AtomSet.cc [GraphModel]: ostream output moved
	to namespace std with the others.

	* lib/AbstractModel.cc [GraphModel]: Bug correction.  Residue
	pointers are erased by specialized model classes.

2004-12-27  Martin Larose  <larosem@onyx.glyphe.net>

	* lib/GraphModel.h, lib/GraphModel.cc [GraphModel]: GraphModel
	should be complete and ready now.

	* lib/Graph.h [GraphModel]: Added iterators on edges and their
	typedefs.

	* lib/Exception.h, lib/Exception.cc [GraphModel]:
	NoSuchElementException parent is now IntLibException.

	* lib/UndirectedGraph.h [GraphModel]: Certain typedef moved to
	protected access (they concerned internal structures).

	* lib/Residue.h, lib/Residue.cc [GraphModel]: ostream operator<< put
	in global namespace.

	* lib/Relation.h, lib/Relation.cc [GraphModel]:
	reassignResiduePointers method added to re-adjust Residue pointers
	when Relation is cloned.  New addPairingLabels method; it seperates
	the labeling from the maximum flow code.

	* lib/OrientedGraph.h [GraphModel]: Certain typedef moved to
	protected access (they concerned internal structures).

	* lib/Model.h, lib/Model.cc [GraphModel]: Bug correction on clone
	and copy construction methods.  Exceptions added.

	* lib/HBond.h, lib/HBond.cc [GraphModel]: ostream operator<< put in
	global namespace.  Added clone method.  Added
	reassignResiduePointers to re-adjust residue pointer from cloned
	GraphModel.  Exceptions added.

	* lib/GraphModel.h, lib/GraphModel.cc [GraphModel]: More complete
	GraphModel class.  Still not completed.

	* lib/Graph.h [GraphModel]: less_deref moved to Algo header file.
	NoSuchElementException moved to Exception header file.

	* lib/Exception.h, lib/Exception.cc [GraphModel]: ostream operator<<
	put in global namespace.  NoSuchElementException&,
	ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException and NullPointerException added.
	Messages types replaced with string.

	* lib/Algo.h [GraphModel]: less_deref binary operator moved in Algo.

	* lib/AbstractModel.h [GraphModel]: ostream operator<< put in global
	namespace.  Exception ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException added on
	operator[].

	* lib/AbstractModel.cc [GraphModel]: ostream operator<< put in
	global namespace.

