2004-12-06  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* RnamlWriter.cc, RnamlReader.cc, RiboseEstimator.cc, Residue.h, Residue.cc, Relation.cc, PropertyType.h, Pdbstream.h, Pdbstream.cc, Molecule.h, Molecule.cc, Model.h, Model.cc, Makefile.in, HomogeneousTransfo.h, HomogeneousTransfo.cc, ExtendedResidue.h, ExtendedResidue.cc, AtomTypeStore.h, AtomTypeStore.cc, AtomType.h, AtomType.cc, Algo.h:
	version 1.5

2004-12-06  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* TypeRepresentationTables.h: Minor changes.

2004-12-03  sebastienl  <sebastienl@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Pdbstream.cc: A ResidueType is only converted from RNA (the
	default) to DNA if a deoxyribose is found instead of simply in
	absence of a O2'.

	* AtomTypeStore.cc: Corrected a compilation warning in
	AtomTypeStore.cc.

	* AtomTypeStore.cc, AtomTypeStore.h, AtomType.h: Changed the
	getVDWR, getAmberEpsilon and getAmberCharge methods to require a
	ResidueType instead of a Residue.  This creates a new problem: the
	type is not sufficient to distinguish terminal residues.  Parameters
	currently assumes that no residue is terminal.

2004-12-02  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Pdbstream.h, Pdbstream.cc: Type representations are loaded on
	demand and not on Pdbstream initialization which causes bugs
	depending on class loading order.

	* ResidueType.h, ResidueType.cc: Static object ResidueTypeStore
	corrected to pointer.  class declaration on object is buggy.

	* AtomType.h, AtomType.cc: Static object AtomTypeStore corrected to
	pointer.  class declaration on object is buggy.

2004-11-25  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Residue.cc, MaximumFlowGraph.h, Graph.h: Removed values.h.

	* Algo.h: HUGE replaced with standard C++ numeric_limits<float>::max().

2004-11-22  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Makefile.in: Apple darwin configuration completed.

	* Makefile.in: LIBEXT variable added.

	* HBond.cc: _GLIBCPP_USE_C99 defined for isnan (patch for darwin).

2004-11-22  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Pdbstream.h, Pdbstream.cc: Potential memory leak corrected in
	oPdbstream::setAtomSet().  Dynamic object ownership should be
	revised in Pdbstream.

2004-11-19  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* RiboseEstimator.cc: MAXFLOAT replaced with standard C++
	numeric_limits<float>::max().

	* sockstream.cc: Added Darwin gcc test.

	* HBond.cc: cmath header file added.

	* Binstream.cc: cstring header file added.

2004-10-15  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* TypeRepresentationTables.cc, RnamlWriter.cc, Atom.cc: minor
	corrections

	* Pdbstream.h, Pdbstream.cc: added static methods
	parse{Residue,Atom}Type({const char*, const string&}) and
	stringify{Residue,Atom}Type (Type*)

	* ResidueTypeStore.h, ResidueTypeStore.cc, ResidueType.h, ResidueType.cc, PropertyTypeStore.h, PropertyTypeStore.cc, PropertyType.h, PropertyType.cc, AtomTypeStore.h, AtomTypeStore.cc, AtomType.h, AtomType.cc:
	Implementation now uses STL string instead of C-style char*.
	External view unchanged except:
	  1- toString() (and toLongString() for residue types) returns a
       	     reference to a STL string. operator const char* () can still be
             used.
	  2- static method AtomType::getColor() now moved within atom type
	     classes.
	  3- atom types aliases removed (ex. 2H5 == H25 == H5** etc.), only
	     standard notation is matched.
	  4- added different is[typename]() method in property types.
	  5- augmented propertytype hierarchy with families BaseOrientation,
	     RiboseOrientation, Face, PuckerMode and GlycosylMode

2004-10-08  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Residue.h, Residue.cc, ExtendedResidue.h, ExtendedResidue.cc:
	* Removed AtomType::less comparator in Residue's atom map. Comparison is made by atomtype pointer address.
	* Friendship with inner iterator classes upgraded to both ways.
	* Bug correction in erase(iterator) implementation.
	* Removed erase(const_iterator).
	* Removed addHLP().
	* addHydrogens() and addLonePairs() takes a boolean parameter to force atom overwritting (default is to overwrite).
	* New static methods nitrogenType19(ResidueType*), carbonType24(ResidueType*) and carbonType68(ResidueType*)
	  that selects the appropriate nucleic acid atom depending on passed residue type's family (purine or pyrimidine).
	* Ribose building major implementation modification:
	    - 5' branch construction places also O1P and O2P along.
	    - Removed static method createPhosphate5p().
	    - Removed all buildRiboseByCCM4D methods and renamed buildRiboseByCCM2D() to buildRiboseByCCM().
	    - Added the possibility to pass a referential to override the calculation in the init phase
	      (useful in the case of a basic Residue that doesn't remember its referential)

2004-10-07  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* AtomType.h: AtomType::less comparator nows checks for null
	pointers and uses AtomType::pNull instead.

2004-10-04  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* ResidueTypeStore.h, ResidueTypeStore.cc, ResidueType.h, Pdbstream.h, Pdbstream.cc, Makefile.in, AtomType.h:
	New pdb output system.  It consist of context tables for input and
	output inserter in Pdbstream.

	* TypeRepresentationTables.h, TypeRepresentationTables.cc: New pdb
	output system.  It consist of context tables for input and output.

2004-09-30  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Pdbstream.cc, AtomTypeStore.h, AtomType.h: Added toAmberString
	method.

2004-09-29  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* ResidueTypeStore.h, ResidueTypeStore.cc, ResidueType.h, ResidueType.cc:
	Added new specialized ribose types for endpoint ribose building:
	  - ResidueType::r{R,D}Ribose5  for 5' startpoint
	  - ResidueType::r{R,D}Ribose3  for 3' endpoint
	  - ResidueType::r{R,D}Ribose53 for a single residue strand (both start and end)

	* AtomSet.h, AtomSet.cc: Added string representation to atomset.
	Added static method create(char*) that creates a new atomset based
	on string representation.

	* Atom.cc: default type set to AtomType::aNull

2004-09-27  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* ResidueTypeStore.h, ResidueType.h: Addition of the Amber
	ResidueType class.

2004-09-24  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* ResidueTypeStore.h, ResidueTypeStore.cc: R?, R?5, R?3, D?, D?5 and
	D?3 types added for ? = A, C, G, U and T.

	* Relation.cc: The list of pairing patterns should be returned as
	const.

	* Pdbstream.h, Pdbstream.cc: Pdb type for Amber is added and output
	differs on the kind.

	* PairingPattern.h: The list of pairing patterns should be returned
	as const.

	* HBond.h, HBond.cc: writeAmberRestraints moved to toleap.

	* AtomTypeStore.h, AtomType.h: Test added on oPdbstream type.

2004-09-19  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* PairingPattern.cc: Changed verbosity level to 5.  Level 3 is WAY
	to much infos for simple program debugging.

	* stlio.h: PrintLn added.

	* PairingPattern.h, PairingPattern.cc: Bug corrections.

	* ResidueTypeStore.cc, PropertyTypeStore.cc, AtomTypeStore.cc:
	Correction of deallocation function.

2004-09-17  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* PairingPattern.cc: return statement omitted.

2004-09-16  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* PairingPattern.cc: Pairing description has changed to bundle
	informations.

