	- Added new property type Null to wrap the eventual null pointer.
	- Slight modification in string type parsing implementation.

2004-07-12  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@yeti.iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Residue.cc, Relation.cc: Warning message levels downgraded to 3
	when atoms are missing.

	* lib/Relation.cc, lib/HBond.cc: The annotation methods trap
	NoSuchAtomException and send a warning message when a mandatory atom
	is missing.

	* lib/Residue.h, lib/Residue.cc, lib/ExtendedResidue.h, lib/ExtendedResidue.cc:
	New public method safeFind(AtomType*) that either finds the
	requested atom or throw a NoSuchAtomException

	* lib/Exception.h, lib/Exception.cc: New exception class
	NoSuchAtomException extends IntLibException.  Thrown when a
	mandatory atom is not found.

