2004-06-30  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/sockstream.cc, lib/SymmetricalMatrix.cc, lib/ServerSocket.cc, lib/RiboseOptimizer5D.cc, lib/RiboseOptimizer2D.cc, lib/RiboseEstimator.cc, lib/RiboseBuilder.cc, lib/ResidueType.h, lib/ResidueType.cc, lib/Residue.h, lib/Residue.cc, lib/ResIdSet.h, lib/ResIdSet.cc, lib/ResId.h, lib/ResId.cc, lib/Relation.cc, lib/PropertyType.h, lib/PropertyType.cc, lib/PairingPattern.cc, lib/Makefile.in, lib/HomogeneousTransfo.cc, lib/ExtendedResidue.cc, lib/AtomType.h, lib/AtomType.cc:
