	* ResidueTypeImp.h, Residue.h, Residue.cc, Model.h, Model.cc, McCore.cc, Graph.h, Graph.cc, CTransfo.cc, CResidue.h, CResidue.cc, CResIdSet.cc, CPoint3D.cc, CHBond.h, CHBond.cc, AbstractResidue.h, AbstractResidue.cc:
	Added CHBond computation involving CH3 on thymine.

