	* stamp-h.in, Makefile.in: stamp-h.in added for config.h making.

2001-09-20  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc: placeIt places all atoms, so no
	parameter is required.

	* lib/Algo.cc: Unneeded file.

	* lib/zfilebuf.h, lib/sockbuf.h, lib/sockbuf.cc, lib/oMessagestream.h, lib/ServerSocket.cc, lib/Messagestream.h, lib/Makefile.in, lib/CPoint3D.cc, configure.in, configure, config.h.in, Makefile.in:
	SGI compatibility updates.

	* ChangeLog: Sourceforge CVS test.

2001-09-14  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/CResidue.cc: Bug corrected.  mAtomRes must be resized before
	any return, if not, a place in a misc atom causes a seg fault.

2001-09-13  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* CResidue.cc: Bug corrected.  The index counter must be increased
	only when an atom is pushed in the residue.

	* CResidue.cc: Html format removed from output.

