	contains the insertion code.

2001-08-24  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* sockbuf.h, sockbuf.cc: Errors are now handled by socket exceptions.
	Added access method GetSocketId().

	* ServerSocket.h, ServerSocket.cc: Errors are now handled with
	socket exceptions.  Removed call to shutdown(), which is
	inappropriate on an unconnected socket.  Added access methods
	GetSocketId() and GetPort().

	* CException.h, CException.cc: Added new Exceptions
	CSocketException and CFatalSocketException

