	Copyright notice includes Universit de Montral.

2001-08-08  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CAtom.cc: fixed a minor bug in class constructors

2001-07-25  Sebastien Lemieux  <lemieuxs@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CHBond.cc: Reactivated method 'DumpAmberRestraints'.

	* McCore.h, McCore.cc: Modified the function 'rmsd_with_align' to
	take two pairs of templated iterator.  The only constraint on the
	iterators is that they should be dereferencable to 'CAtom's.  This
	allows to compute RMSD on any type of container and both on CAtom*
	or CResidue::iterator.  The function was split between the .h and
	.cc to minimize the compilation effort...

	* CHBond.cc, Algo.h, Algo.cc: dummy

	* CResidue.h: Added data member 'mExternalIndex' with Get/Set.

	* Pdbstream.cc: Removed the possibility to write 'HETATM' in
	function 'putatom'.  Interfer with the use of rt_Misc in 'toleap'
	package.

2001-07-16  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Algo.h: FLT_MAX replaced with HUGE.

2001-07-05  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CResidue.cc, CResidue.h, sockbuf.h:
	Corrected the AtomCopy function so that iterators stay valid

2001-06-21  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* Algo.h, CHBond.cc, CHBond.h, CModel.h, DirectedGraph.h, McCore.cc, McCore.h:
	Modified CHBond and added an inheritance from HBond, which is a symbolic description only

2001-05-29  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CHBond.h, CModel.cc, CModel.h, CResidue.cc, CResidue.h, CTransfo.cc, CTransfo.h, DirectedGraph.cc, DirectedGraph.h, Makefile.in, McCore.cc, McCore.h, CAtom.cc, CAtom.h, CHBond.cc:
